  Tc 1.1998  Tw (our modern day and age. A place is left for work on a honorary basis and for volunteer work. Very few ) TjT* -0.0468  Tc 0.4068  Tw (people, however, would be con) Tj125.76 0  TD -0.0611  Tc 0.1211  Tw (sidered too old to work at the age of fifty. At that point, however, the burden ) Tj-125.76 -11.52  TD -0.0715  Tc 1.4421  Tw (of responsibility was lifted from them. Those who kept on working did it, not because they had to, but ) Tj0 -11.52  TD -0.1167  Tc -0.0033  Tw (because  they wanted to. ) Tj98.4 0  TD 0  Tc -0.12  Tw ( ) Tj-98.4 -11.52  TD ( ) Tj36 0  TD -0.079  Tc 0.7057  Tw (It has been said that there is no retirement f) Tj176.64 0  TD -0.0625  Tc 0.3789  Tw (or a servant of the Lord, this verse seems to contradict ) Tj-212.64 -11.52  TD -0.0918  Tc 0.7355  Tw (this. The Lord allows for the fact that the burden may become too heavy and that there is a point at which ) Tj0 -11.04  TD -0.1127  Tc 1.1687  Tw (we may simple draw back and enjoy what we do and what we are. Having come at this place in m) Tj407.04 0  TD -0.1994  Tc 0.5594  Tw (y own ) Tj-407.04 -11.52  TD -0.0306  Tc 0.328  Tw (life, I found out that this is one of the hardest positions to maintain. It is so much more difficult to sit back ) Tj0 -11.52  TD -0.0469  Tc 1.3935  Tw (and enjoy ourselves, without feeling guilty about it, than to lose ourselves in all kinds of activities and ) TjT* -0.095  Tc -0.025  Tw (responsibilities. Evidently,) Tj105.6 0  TD -0.0465  Tc -0.0735  Tw ( God wants us to know that His burden is light.) Tj187.2 0  TD 0  Tc -0.12  Tw ( ) TjETendstreamendobj151 0 obj3600 endobj152 0 obj<< /Type /Page /Parent 146 0 R /Resources << /Font << /F0 6 0 R /F1 8 0 R /F2 12 0 R >> /ProcSet 2 0 R >> /Contents 153 0 R >> endobj153 0 obj<< /Length 154 0 R >> stream
